org.teatrove.teaservlet.util
Class FilteredServletContext

java.lang.Object
  org.teatrove.teaservlet.util.FilteredServletContext
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.servlet.ServletContext
public class FilteredServletContext
extends Object
implements javax.servlet.ServletContext

A ServletContext wrapper that passes all calls to an internal ServletContext. This class is designed for subclasses to override or hook into the behavior of a ServletContext instance.

Author:
Brian S O'Neill
